analysis.summary: This document is a compilation of seven analytical articles from various publications discussing Middle East politics during the Arab Spring, covering topics including Afghanistan negotiations, Syrian protests, Egyptian foreign policy shifts, Fatah-Hamas unity, and the Muslim Brotherhood's political organization in post-Mubarak Egypt.
